        </item>
        <item>
            <title>中国八宝粥：可当小米镜头盖配件，整埋「小米 14 Ultra 专业摄影套装」够识玩 </title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/16/xiaomi-14-ultra-camera-cover/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=xiaomi-14-ultra-camera-cover</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/16/xiaomi-14-ultra-camera-cover/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 07:55:57 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1224757</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>中国一个八宝粥品牌银鹭，旗下的罐装甜品的盖掩，被指可当成小米 14 Ultra 相机的镜头盖。银鹭网路小编马上出招，呼吁小米用家一定要用八宝粥盖子当成小米镜头盖，并称他们的盖子是「严丝无缝、完美适配（编辑按：合衬）」。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224758" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/f5abb08595f3c6e1-694x553.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="553" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/f5abb08595f3c6e1-694x553.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/f5abb08595f3c6e1.jpg 1129w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Xiaomi 14 Ultra 背面相机颇为巨大，建有 Leica Summilux 四镜头模组，并采用 5000 万像素 1 吋感光元件，附有 F1.63~F4 无段可变光圈，其他镜头都支援 5000 万像素高解像度摄影。有网民发现，中国食品品牌银鹭旗下八宝粥产品的盖子，刚好可贴合这个庞大突出的相机模组。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1224759" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/30e9a65f382d0bd-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/30e9a65f382d0bd-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/30e9a65f382d0bd-scaled.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>银鹭的网路小编马上发挥创意，更加将八宝粥盖子拿到小米专门店拍摄了一辑相片。在经过该小编实测后，证明盖子「严丝无缝」，完美地盖在 Xiaomi 14 Ultra 的镜头组之上。网民指以后也不用担心跌烂相机镜头了。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.cnbeta.com.tw/articles/tech/1422816.htm">CNBETA</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/30/redmi-buds-5-pro-review/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Redmi Buds 5 Pro　外形　佩戴感　功能　音质开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/16/xiaomi-might-launch-an-8-inch-tablet/notebook/tablet-notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">多名高层微博爆料，小米 8 吋平板料短期发表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/07/mi14-mi14ultra-hk-price-revealed/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【报价】小米 14 + 小米 14 Ultra 港行正式推出	首「卖大包」送摄影套装 + 抵玩定价公布</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/16/xiaomi-14-ultra-camera-cover/mobile-phone/">中国八宝粥：可当小米镜头盖配件，整埋「小米 14 Ultra 专业摄影套装」够识玩 </a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
